ActBusiness Development Bank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of ERIC BOYKO of Île des Soeurs, Quebec, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Léandre Cormier, effective August 29, 2007.
